.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH create 1  "create " 
.SH NAME
create \- Create a synchronized folder
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcreate\fR [\fB\-\-prefix\fR] [\fB\-\-mode\fR] [\fB\-\-relay\-fallback\fR] [\fB\-\-network\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIPATH\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Create a synchronized folder
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-prefix\fR \fI<PREFIX>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-mode\fR \fI<MODE>\fR [default: sendreceive]

.TP
\fB\-\-relay\-fallback\fR
Enable Syncthing relay fallback for this folder
.TP
\fB\-\-network\fR \fI<NETWORK>\fR
Add the created folder to a named network
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIPATH\fR] [default: .]

